00:39:25,071 --> 00:39:26,781
How I wish…

549
00:39:26,864 --> 00:39:29,658
How I wish I didn't force you
to talk to me at that time.

550
00:39:29,742 --> 00:39:31,285
I should have…

551
00:39:31,369 --> 00:39:33,996
I should have waited
for your anger towards me to subside.

552
00:39:36,040 --> 00:39:37,375
I'm sorry.

553
00:39:38,376 --> 00:39:39,502
Sofia, please.

554
00:39:39,585 --> 00:39:40,836
I'm not the killer.

555
00:39:40,920 --> 00:39:42,505
No. Please, please.

556
00:39:42,588 --> 00:39:44,215
No, please.

557
00:39:44,298 --> 00:39:48,094
Ward and I are just the same.

558
00:39:48,177 --> 00:39:50,346
Remember, Ward was framed too.

559
00:39:50,429 --> 00:39:52,765
That's what has happened
to me now. I'm innocent,

560
00:39:52,848 --> 00:39:53,974
Believe me.

561
00:39:54,058 --> 00:39:56,769
I only saw the gas mask
in my things last night.

562
00:39:56,852 --> 00:39:58,187
I have no idea how it happened.

563
00:39:58,270 --> 00:39:59,313
Sofia, please.

564
00:39:59,397 --> 00:40:01,065
Believe me, my dear.

565
00:40:01,148 --> 00:40:02,024
Mommy…

566
00:40:02,108 --> 00:40:03,192
What? Believe me.

567
00:40:03,275 --> 00:40:05,486
Tell me you believe me.

568
00:40:05,569 --> 00:40:08,072
Why didn't you tell me right away?

569
00:40:09,949 --> 00:40:12,034
Because I got scared.

570
00:40:12,576 --> 00:40:13,994
I didn't know what to do.

571
00:40:14,078 --> 00:40:16,705
I didn't know how
you were going to react, Sofia.

572
00:40:16,789 --> 00:40:19,333
I got scared
that you might not believe me.

573
00:40:19,417 --> 00:40:21,335
And look. That's what has happened.

574
00:40:21,419 --> 00:40:23,629
You don't believe me.

575
00:40:23,712 --> 00:40:25,339
Sofia, I'm not the killer.

576
00:40:25,423 --> 00:40:27,591
- It's not me.
- Mommy…

577
00:40:29,385 --> 00:40:31,137
George, forgive me.

578
00:40:32,388 --> 00:40:33,973
Please forgive me.

579
00:40:37,518 --> 00:40:38,978
I forgive you now.

580
00:40:41,647 --> 00:40:43,023
Thank you.

581
00:40:44,442 --> 00:40:45,776
Thank you…

582
00:40:57,079 --> 00:40:58,372
Sofia…

583
00:40:58,456 --> 00:41:00,291
I'm sorry. I'm sorry, okay.

584
00:41:00,958 --> 00:41:02,960
I was just shocked.

585
00:41:04,879 --> 00:41:06,213
But we need to tell Sergeant Royales

586
00:41:06,297 --> 00:41:07,756
about the gas mask.

587
00:41:07,840 --> 00:41:09,508
Like when George did.

588
00:41:09,592 --> 00:41:11,886
We need to prove that
you were just framed up,

589
00:41:11,969 --> 00:41:13,762
No, no, no.

590
00:41:13,846 --> 00:41:15,848
They will not believe me, Sofia.

591
00:41:15,931 --> 00:41:18,350
They will not believe me, please.

592
00:41:18,434 --> 00:41:20,311
Because…

593
00:41:20,394 --> 00:41:22,354
the night when Francis got run over,

594
00:41:22,438 --> 00:41:24,231
I was just here at home.

595
00:41:24,315 --> 00:41:25,983
No one saw me.

596
00:41:26,066 --> 00:41:27,693
I have no alibi.

597
00:41:27,776 --> 00:41:30,779
You were Ward's alibi
because you were together in a motel.

598
00:41:30,863 --> 00:41:33,574
But me, I was all alone here.

599
00:41:33,657 --> 00:41:35,576
So, no one can prove that I was here.

600
00:41:35,659 --> 00:41:37,870
And they are all mad at me here.

601
00:41:37,953 --> 00:41:40,372
So please, don't tell them.

602
00:41:40,456 --> 00:41:42,500
- Mom…
- No.

603
00:41:42,583 --> 00:41:43,501
What are we going to do?

604
00:41:50,799 --> 00:41:51,967
I don't know.

605
00:41:52,051 --> 00:41:53,427
I don't know what to do.

606
00:41:54,345 --> 00:41:55,554
But Sofia,

607
00:41:55,638 --> 00:41:57,723
we need to dispose of the gas mask.

608
00:41:57,806 --> 00:41:59,725
How are we going to do that?

609
00:42:02,645 --> 00:42:03,854
Aurora.

610
00:42:03,938 --> 00:42:05,689
Let's put this in Aurora's things.

611
00:42:05,773 --> 00:42:07,399
What? Mom.

612
00:42:07,483 --> 00:42:09,068
You would frame her?

613
00:42:09,151 --> 00:42:10,319
No.

614
00:42:10,402 --> 00:42:13,405
Sofia, you saw how

615
00:42:13,489 --> 00:42:15,366
that woman insulted me.

616
00:42:15,449 --> 00:42:17,785
This is my chance to get back at her.

617
00:42:17,868 --> 00:42:19,036
Let's put this in her things.

618
00:42:19,119 --> 00:42:20,788
Mom, if that's your plan,

619
00:42:20,871 --> 00:42:23,290
I will not help you.

620
00:42:23,874 --> 00:42:25,376
If you don't want to, then don't.

621
00:42:49,233 --> 00:42:51,485
I'm scared, Sofia.

622
00:42:51,569 --> 00:42:53,487
<i>- Mom, just tell them the truth.</i>
<i>- I'm scared.</i>

623
00:42:54,071 --> 00:42:55,990
<i>That's all you need to do.</i>

624
00:42:56,574 --> 00:42:58,075
<i>Amando…</i>

625
00:42:58,158 --> 00:42:59,952
For not protecting me from Galvan.

626
00:43:00,035 --> 00:43:01,787
NEXT EPISODE

627
00:43:01,870 --> 00:43:03,414
You deserve that.

628
00:43:03,497 --> 00:43:05,332
My OB is just near here.

629
00:43:05,416 --> 00:43:07,626
She's available for me anytime.

630
00:43:07,710 --> 00:43:09,420
<i>I'd love to help you.</i>

631
00:43:09,503 --> 00:43:11,589
<i>I want to be a part of your journey</i>

632
00:43:11,672 --> 00:43:12,840
<i>to becoming a mom.</i>

633
00:43:12,923 --> 00:43:14,758
I have a bigger revelation.

634
00:43:14,842 --> 00:43:17,177
Rebecca is the daughter of Ma'am Aurora.

635
00:43:17,261 --> 00:43:18,637
What did you say?

636
00:43:20,097 --> 00:43:21,974
Is what the staff is saying true?

637
00:43:22,057 --> 00:43:24,351
Rebecca is the daughter
of Aurora and your father?

638
00:43:24,435 --> 00:43:25,978
You will cover for your father?

639
00:43:26,061 --> 00:43:27,062
Thank you, Kate.

640
00:43:27,146 --> 00:43:29,064
I can now push through with my plan.

641
00:43:29,148 --> 00:43:31,942
Plan? What plan?
